net.floodlightcontroller.debugevent

Class EventResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.debugevent.EventResource

  • public class EventResource
extends java.lang.Object
    Event Instance of a particular event category. This is only for REST purpose. Actual Event class consists of Object of Event. Here we parse it into its string form using getCustomFormatter and return for REST and CLI.
